# Minimal deployment environment for the Dokploy compose stack.
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. Do NOT commit the real `.env`.
#
# Optional variables for notifications, auth hardening, Google sign-in, and
# Traefik overrides are documented in `docs/deployment.md` and
# `docs/notifications.md`.

# Public hostname Traefik routes to (web at /, push-api at /api).
# Use a real domain in production — push notifications / PWA require HTTPS.
APP_HOST=todo.example.com
